Fixed a cosmetic bug in
:class:`lino.modlib.notes.models.Note`:
when trying to print a note with an empty 
`type` field, this caused an
:ref:`ise`
"AttributeError: 'NoneType' object has no attribute 'body_template'
at /api/pcsw/NotesByPerson".


New virtual column `contract_company` in :ddref:`welfare.pcsw.Client`.


